When SSH'ing into the OP Staions use -Y

Using vim 
use :set nonu  to unset line numbers for copying
delete lines using :(start line number) (end line number) d
SHIFT+O to go over line
o to go under linesyntax enable
set tabstop=4
set shiftwidth=4
set expandtab
set number
filetype indent on
set autoindent

